### 9.8 Link model (revised)

Because many layers now point to external systems, the link layer becomes even more important.

#### `link_edge`

- `id` (UUID)
- `user_id`
- `source_type`
- `source_id`
- `target_type`
- `target_id`
- `link_type`
- `confidence`
- `explanation`
- `created_at`
- `created_by` (`system`, `user`)

Supported `target_type` values should now include:
- `journal_entry`
- `extracted_item`
- `knowledge_node`
- `public_artifact`
- `media_artifact`
- `project_ref`
